(615, 1, '2012-11-27 01:46:31', '2012-11-27 01:46:31', '<div class="line_plus"></div>\r\n<p>Through our own practice experience and our work in assessing and valuing successful veterinary practices, we are able to offer advice on a broad range of practice marketing issues. On a daily basis, we see first hand “what works” and “what doesn’t” in a marketing sense.</p>\r\n<p>In a similar context, we are able to give a considered professional opinion on practice strategic options including practice expansion, specialisation, mergers and conglomeration.</p>\r\n<div class="line_plus"></div>', 'Practice Marketing and Strategies', '', 'publish', 'open', 'open', '', 'practice-marketing-and-strategies', '', '', '2012-11-29 01:52:52', '2012-11-29 01:52:52', '', 597, 'http://valuvet.com.au/_dev3/?page_id=615', 0, 'page', '', 0),
