(792, 1, '2012-11-27 01:44:54', '2012-11-27 01:44:54', 'Much of our work involves valuing practices for either entry or exit of partners. This makes us familiar with the many different working and business arrangements within partnerships, and the factors that make them successful or unsuccessful.\r\n\r\nWe are always happy to share our knowledge with colleagues who are contemplating shared working or ownership arrangements.\r\n\r\nOur consultants Dr Tony Thelander and Dr Hugh White have over a 80 years of combined practical veterinary and business experience within the industry. Our current work involves consulting in all aspects of veterinary practice so we are able to share our industry perspective with those veterinarians considering career changes within the profession.', 'Partnerships and Career Advice', '', 'inherit', 'open', 'open', '', '613-revision-2', '', '', '2012-11-27 01:44:54', '2012-11-27 01:44:54', '', 613, 'http://valuvet.com.au/_dev3/613-revision-2/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
(625, 1, '2012-11-27 01:55:17', '2012-11-27 01:55:17', '<div class="frame_quote">\r\n[blockquote]<p>ValuVet''s primary mission is to improve value in our clients'' practices by enhancing the management of those practices and in addition, to facilitate the sale of practices and of partnerships.</p>[/blockquote]\r\n</div>\r\n<div class="line_plus"></div>\r\n<h4>In achieving our mission, we strive to:</h4>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n<li>Offer the most comprehensive service in all aspects of our consultancy</li>\r\n<li>Improve the quality of the lives of our clients, of your staff and the quality of the practices we visit</li>\r\n<li>Generate an increased financial return for our clients</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<h4>We work closely with you</h4>\r\n<p>No matter how large or small your veterinary practice, we understand the importance of working collaboratively. With our stability, geographic reach, maturity, depth of knowledge and experience, we are well placed to assist you.</p>\r\n\r\n<h4>Valuations</h4>\r\n<p>The basic premise of ValuVet is to provide a consistent, reliable and relevant practice valuation service and to provide clients with assistance in selling or buying practices. This service includes goodwill and equipment valuations, full practice appraisals for purpose of sale and our practice marketplace listing. In addition to this, we are also committed to providing services to our clients which will help them to achieve their business and financial goals in practice.</p>\r\n\r\n<h6><em>Please feel free to navigate our site to find more information on our products and services.</em></h6>', 'About ValuVet', '', 'publish', 'open', 'closed', '', 'valuvet', '', '', '2012-11-28 01:51:51', '2012-11-28 01:51:51', '', 627, 'http://valuvet.com.au/_dev3/?page_id=625', 0, 'page', '', 0),
