(759, 1, '2012-11-28 01:15:05', '2012-11-28 01:15:05', '<div class="line_plus"></div>\r\n<p>ValuVet''s primary mission is to improve value in our clients’ practices by enhancing the management of those practices and in addition, to facilitate the sale of practices and of partnerships.</p>\r\nIn achieving our mission, we strive to:\r\noffer the most comprehensive service in all aspects of our consultancy\r\nimprove the quality of the lives of our clients, of your staff and the quality of the practices we visit\r\ngenerate an increased financial return for our clients\r\nWe work closely with you\r\nNo matter how large or small your veterinary practice, we understand the importance of working collaboratively. With our stability, geographic reach, maturity, depth of knowledge and experience, we are well placed to assist you.\r\n\r\nValuations\r\nThe basic premise of ValuVet is to provide a consistent, reliable and relevant practice valuation service and to provide clients with assistance in selling or buying practices. This service includes goodwill and equipment valuations, full practice appraisals for purpose of sale and our practice marketplace listing. In addition to this, we are also committed to providing services to our clients which will help them to achieve their business and financial goals in practice.\r\n\r\nPlease feel free to navigate our site to find more information on our products and services.', 'About ValuVet', '', 'inherit', 'open', 'open', '', '625-revision-6', '', '', '2012-11-28 01:15:05', '2012-11-28 01:15:05', '', 625, 'http://valuvet.com.au/_dev3/625-revision-6/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
