(808, 1, '2012-11-27 01:36:46', '2012-11-27 01:36:46', '\r\n<p>Our practice valuations generally consist of three major components. These are a financial assessment, an evaluation of equipment and a practice report. In combination, these provide the practice principals with a comprehensive assessment of the worth of the business and its different components. This, in turn, allows the principals to enter into negotiations with prospective purchasers or incoming partners, to approach finance companies or to revisit strategic planning with confidence based on a sound evaluation of worth.</p>\r\n\r\nFor more information on these services please click on the links provided below.\r\n<ul>\r\n<li>Valuation – Practice Appraisals</li>\r\n<li>Valuation – Financial Assessment</li>\r\n<li>Valuation – Equipment Assessment</li>\r\n<li>Practice Assessments</li>\r\n<li>Partnerships & Career Advice</li>\r\n<li>Practice Marketing & Strategies</li>\r\n<li>Buying and Selling Practices</li>\r\n</ul>', 'Valuations', '', 'inherit', 'open', 'open', '', '599-revision-3', '', '', '2012-11-27 01:36:46', '2012-11-27 01:36:46', '', 599, 'http://valuvet.com.au/_dev3/599-revision-3/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
(809, 1, '2012-11-28 15:21:20', '2012-11-28 15:21:20', '<div class="line_plus"></div>\n<p>During the course of the practice visit, our assessors will list all equipment in the practice. This equipment is later itemized and has a value assigned to each item. An equipment schedule is provided in conjunction with all practice valuations unless otherwise requested.</p>\n<p>The equipment valuation is based on market value rather than depreciated tax value because we feel this has much greater relevance to both vendors and purchasers.</p>\n<p>Revaluing equipment may initially appear to have some taxation ramifications for the vendor, however, the Small Business Capital Gains Tax Exemption provisions generally resolve this issue.</p>\n', 'Equipment Assessment', '', 'inherit', 'open', 'open', '', '607-autosave', '', '', '2012-11-28 15:21:20', '2012-11-28 15:21:20', '', 607, 'http://valuvet.com.au/_dev3/607-autosave/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
