(816, 1, '2012-11-27 01:39:40', '2012-11-27 01:39:40', 'Financial Assessment\r\nThis is based on analysis of your financial data and on a myriad of data relating to financial performance. We provide you with a list of information which we ask you to collect and send to us prior to our visit. We consider an on-site inspection to be an essential component of the valuation. In-depth interviews with principals and with staff provide us with a true understanding of the various factors which affect the value of goodwill. From this visit, we are able to combine with our experienced accountants to come up with an assessment of practice goodwill.\r\n\r\nOver the years and with over 500 practice valuations performed, we have built an extensive database of ‘real-world’ sale values. From this, we are able to provide a very realistic assessment of the worth of your practice.', 'Financial Assessment', '', 'inherit', 'open', 'open', '', '604-revision-3', '', '', '2012-11-27 01:39:40', '2012-11-27 01:39:40', '', 604, 'http://valuvet.com.au/_dev3/604-revision-3/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
(817, 1, '2012-11-28 15:05:04', '2012-11-28 15:05:04', '<p>Through our own practice experience and our work in assessing and valuing successful veterinary practices, we are able to offer advice on a broad range of practice marketing issues. On a daily basis, we see first hand “what works” and “what doesn’t” in a marketing sense.</p>\r\n<p>In a similar context, we are able to give a considered professional opinion on practice strategic options including practice expansion, specialisation, mergers and conglomeration.</p>\r\n<div class="line_plus"></div>', 'Practice Marketing and Strategies', '', 'inherit', 'open', 'open', '', '615-revision-10', '', '', '2012-11-28 15:05:04', '2012-11-28 15:05:04', '', 615, 'http://valuvet.com.au/_dev3/615-revision-10/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
